This program has been compiled and tested under ubuntu Linux and Windows.

Compile:
  to compile this program, you need to have 
  - bakefile (http://bakefile.sf.net)
  - wxWidgets (http://www.wxwidgets.org)

release build:
 nmake -f makefile.vc DEBUG=0 WX_DEBUG=0

You can install vc++ 2008 express under Windows and use nmake to compile it.

